---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout category="business">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-16">자사 강점</h1>

    <!-- Top Image Banner -->
    <div class="relative">
      <img
        src="/agencies.jpg"
        alt="agencies"
        class="w-full h-auto rounded-md shadow-lg"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-start px-8 bg-black bg-opacity-50 text-white"
      >
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">전국 네트워크</h2>
        <p class="text-sm">
          전국 15개 시도에 주주총회 의결권대리 확보를 위한 촘촘한 네트워크망
          구축
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Four Features -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
      <!-- BEST -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 rounded-full"
        >
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/star--v1.png"
            alt="best icon"
            class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-lg mb-1">BEST</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            원활한 주주총회진행을 위한 종합적인 컨설팅과 효율적인 업무수행
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- EXCELLENCE -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 rounded-full"
        >
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/diamond.png"
            alt="excellence icon"
            class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-lg mb-1">EXCELLENCE</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            관련 법률 검토를 통한 이슈분석, 솔루션 도출
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SPECIALTY -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 rounded-full"
        >
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/handshake.png"
            alt="specialty icon"
            class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-lg mb-1">SPECIALTY</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            경험이 풍부한 전문인력의 효율적 의결권 모집 전문인력을 통한 전략적
            주주총회 진행
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- TRUST -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 rounded-full"
        >
          <img
            src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/like.png"
            alt="trust icon"
            class="w-6 h-6 opacity-70"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-primary font-bold text-lg mb-1">TRUST</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            지속적인 관리로 회사와 주주들에 대한 커뮤니티 형성으로 회사와
            주주가치를 지속적으로 제고
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
